Wooorkie App - Legal Information: Wooorkie App is here to help with workouts. However Wooorkie App will not ask you to pay using any ways except using payments through Apple App Store. Also, Wooorkie App does not require to submit any users personal data. All data inputted by user is stored only locally on users device and in iCloud in that way so Wooorkie App cannot access users data. Wooorkie App cannot be held responsible for any successfull or unsuccessfull notifiying about users inputted data, such as notifications about future workouts or countdowns. 
